      <acqinfo id="aspace_f0b999da61f2d8eaf06e1f8a6a7b7917">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The Collection of Printing Production Materials was housed in the Arts of the Book Collection until its transfer to the Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library in 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_ae093435c9e0e722668f352a295f64b5">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_99a0eb4c3e50b37fbd4b8502210b4f1b">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
